I WILL NEVER FORGET YOU
I took the time to finish pokemon mystery dungeon explorers of time I never realized how beautiful of a...
body:
I WILL NEVER FORGET YOU

I took the time to finish pokemon mystery dungeon explorers of time I never realized how beautiful of a game it can be and i started to think why didnt i even play it when i was a kid.

It was one of the most fun yet most heartbreaking games i’ve ever played and i believe words cant describe how amazing this game is

blog.name: aquilacalvitium
blog.title: Your Triple A Friend
blog.description:
No One Ever Made a Difference by Being Like Everybody Else ----------------------------------------------------------------Hey there! My names are Claire and Aquila (I have two names). I'm an agender 18 year old ace/aro furry and I live in the UK. If you need to rant or complain or whatever, just drop me an ask! You don't have to apologise or ask if it's okay because as far as I'm concerned, as soon as you follow me, you're my friend! And I love receiving messages and asks from my friends!
Please no nsfw and I don't respond to chainmail. Please refrain from any mention of drugs, suicide or self harm, unless you need to vent in which case, feel free to direct message me to keep it private. Bear in mind I am not equipped to help you with your problems, but I am here to listen.
Check out my YouTube channel Aquila Calvitium!
Thanks for stopping by and I hope you have a great rest of your day!

summary: This has been in my wip folder for weeks, but damn if I’m not proud of the end result! As you can probably tell, my favourite...
caption:
This has been in my wip folder for weeks, but damn if I’m not proud of the end result!

As you can probably tell, my favourite pokemon type is grass! And yes, I know it look like Haxorous doesn’t have any legs, but when I was drawing it, I somehow managed to angle its leg so that it was completely hidden behind my fursona.

And yes, I love bulbasaur. Fight me.

p.s. the second image is transparent
